THIRD-PARTY ATTRIBUTION

This project's Discord bot core (command loader, moderation, automod,
antinuke, tickets, giveaways, reaction roles, welcome/farewell, logging, and
most utility/fun/AI commands, under src/bot and src/database) is a modified
derivative of "ASTRYX" by itsfizys (Aegis) (https://github.com/devrock07/astryx),
used and redistributed under the MELON OPEN SOURCE LICENSE reproduced in full
below, per its Section 2 conditions (retain copyright notice, attribute the
author, preserve license terms, document changes). Changes made: rebranded
from ASTRYX to "Infinity Bot"; removed unused music-related dependencies and dead
code; added a warn/case moderation module with auto-escalating punishment;
added a web dashboard.

This project's web dashboard (under dashboard/) is a modified derivative of
the "Zenith" dashboard from Pogy-Bot by devrock07
(https://github.com/devrock07/Pogy-Bot), used with the permission of its
copyright holder. Changes made: rebranded from Pogy/Zenith to "Infinity Bot"; data
layer rewritten from MongoDB/Mongoose to PostgreSQL/Sequelize to match this
project's bot; pages and API routes adapted to this project's feature set
(including tickets, giveaways, reaction roles, and the warn/case system,
which did not exist in the original Zenith dashboard).

